1.title: Meet Shivay and His Brothers
1.plot: Ishqbaaz is a new show about the three Oberoi brothers. Meet Shivaay, whose life's loves are business and his two brothers. Omkara, the second brother is an artist and the youngest Rudra believes life to be all about having fun
